{"tid":1785342,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"高級消防隊長被廉署起訴 涉嫌妨礙司法公正","createTime":"2019-12-16T09:55:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-16T12:00:05.000Z","uid":216992,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"da71301cb50a1649e432956442da36a93418f8c9","tid":1785342,"uid":216992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T09:55:24.000Z","msg":"廉署落案起訴一名消防處高級消防隊長涉嫌妨礙司法公正，隱瞞尖沙咀一間酒吧阻塞逃生途徑的犯罪證據。被告已獲准保釋，周三將在觀塘裁判法院答辯。<br />\n<br />\n廉署早前接獲消防處轉介有關貪污投訴。37歲被告馮國輝，被指涉嫌在去年1月17日及24日，意圖妨礙司法公正而作出傾向妨礙司法公正的行為，現被控兩項罪名。被告案發時在消防處牌照及審批總區轄下的防火執法專隊工作。"},{"pid":"7e3daf385454f3c7a235c3018930ad006d60f966","tid":1785342,"uid":216992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T09:55:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1497962-20191216.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1497962-20191216.htm&d=dVEf9brN%2BTtwApumOSMW7hZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=24879c2b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1497962-20191216.htm&h=60861bf3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1497962-20191216.htm</a>"},{"pid":"7e2a92e3c34f794a61420b1f236cb59d983bdda0","tid":1785342,"uid":30966,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T09:56:12.000Z","msg":"721查成點呀成班垃圾"},{"pid":"1853360755b58b3812eccd5c00abb911fc40c347","tid":1785342,"uid":216992,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T09:56:25.000Z","msg":"又話查721<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n結果呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asset